org.cef.network

Class CefCookieManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cef.network.CefCookieManager

  • public abstract class CefCookieManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used for managing cookies. The methods of this class may be called on any thread unless otherwise indicated.(用于管理Cookie的类。除非另有说明，否则可以在任何线程上调用此类的方法。)

    • Method Detail

      • deleteCookies

        public abstract boolean deleteCookies(java.lang.String url,
                                      java.lang.String cookieName)
        Delete all cookies that match the specified parameters. If both |url| and |cookieName| values are specified all host and domain cookies matching both will be deleted. If only |url| is specified all host cookies (but not domain cookies) irrespective of path will be deleted. If |url| is empty all cookies for all hosts and domains will be deleted. Cookies can alternately be deleted using the visit*Cookies() methods.(删除所有与指定参数匹配的cookie。如果同时指定了|url|和|cookieName|值，则所有与两者匹配的主机和域cookie都将被删除。如果只指定了|url|，则将删除所有主机cookie（而不是域cookie），无论路径如何。如果|url|为空，则所有主机和域的所有cookie都将被删除。Cookie也可以使用visit*Cookies()方法删除。)
        Parameters:
        url - The cookie URL to delete or null.(url-需要删除cookie的url，可以为null。)
        cookieName - The cookie name to delete or null.(cookieName-需要删除的cookie名称，可以为null。)
        Returns:
        False if a non-empty invalid URL is secified or if cookies cannot be accessed.(如果指定了非空的无效URL或无法访问cookie，则返回False。)

      • getGlobalManager

        public static final CefCookieManager getGlobalManager()
        Returns the global cookie manager. By default data will be stored at CefSettings.cache_path if specified or in memory otherwise.(返回全局cookie管理器。默认情况下，如果指定，数据将存储在CefSettings.cache_path中，否则将存储在内存中。)
        Returns:
        The global cookie manager.(全局cookie管理器。)

      • setCookie

        public abstract boolean setCookie(java.lang.String url,
                                  CefCookie cookie)
        Sets a cookie given a valid URL and explicit user-provided cookie attributes. This function expects each attribute to be well-formed. It will check for disallowed characters (e.g. the ';' character is disallowed within the cookie value attribute) and fail without setting the cookie if such characters are found.(在给定有效URL和明确的用户提供的cookie属性的情况下设置cookie。此函数要求每个属性的格式正确。它将检查不允许的字符（例如，cookie值属性中不允许使用“；”字符），如果发现此类字符，则在不设置cookie的情况下失败。)
        Parameters:
        url - The cookie URL.(url-cookie url。)
        cookie - The cookie attributes.(cookie-cookie属性。)
        Returns:
        False if an invalid URL is specified or if cookies cannot be accessed.(如果指定了无效的URL或无法访问cookie，则为False。)

      • visitAllCookies

        public abstract boolean visitAllCookies(CefCookieVisitor visitor)
        Visit all cookies. The returned cookies are ordered by longest path, then by earliest creation date.(访问所有cookie。返回的cookie按最长路径排序，然后按最早创建日期排序。)
        Parameters:
        visitor - Callback that will receive cookies on the UI thread.(visitor-将在UI线程上接收cookie的回调。)
        Returns:
        False if cookies cannot be accessed.(如果无法访问cookie，则为False。)

      • visitUrlCookies

        public abstract boolean visitUrlCookies(java.lang.String url,
                                        boolean includeHttpOnly,
                                        CefCookieVisitor visitor)
        Visit a subset of cookies. The returned cookies are ordered by longest path, then by earliest creation date.(访问cookie的子集。返回的cookie按最长路径排序，然后按最早创建日期排序。)
        Parameters:
        url - Results are filtered by the given url scheme, host, domain and path.(url-根据给定的url方案、主机、域和路径过滤结果。)
        includeHttpOnly - If true HTTP-only cookies will also be included in the results.(includeHttpOnly-如果是真正的HTTP，则结果中也将包含仅Cookie。)
        visitor - Callback that will receive cookies on the UI thread.(visitor-将在UI线程上接收cookie的回调。)
        Returns:
        False if cookies cannot be accessed.(如果无法访问cookie，则为False。)
